**\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nPopulate this sector with useful outreach data without repeating completed work:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n1. Add or improve `company.description` for every company you touch, including companies that already have recruiters.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n2. Populate empty `recruiters[]` arrays where credible public LinkedIn/web evidence exists.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n3. Keep existing recruiter entries unless you can clearly tell they are stale or wrong.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n4. After coverage is complete, deepen companies to a maximum of 10 contacts each.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n5. After existing companies are deepened, add more companies in this sector, prioritizing Miami / South Florida and San Jose / Silicon Valley.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Company Description Standard\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nEvery touched company should have a concise description:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- 18-35 words, one sentence.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Say what the company actually does and where it fits in the sector.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Prefer concrete products, customers, or technical domain over marketing language.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Mention SWE/AI relevance only when it is natural.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- Do not invent facts. If public data is thin, use a conservative description based on the company category and careers/company page.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nExample:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"NVIDIA designs GPUs, AI accelerators, networking hardware, and software platforms used across data centers, gaming, autonomous systems, and applied machine learning.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\